\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 JWT_SECRET
\f0\fs24  on both the IDP and MCP-Mobile workers (must be identical value so tokens verify){\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://github.com/JW-Flo/Project-Ignite/blob/bcc8b784cac1d7962ed21c17e65e0b28a3998130/mcp-idp/wrangler.toml#L30-L37"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 \ul \ulc3 \strokec3 github.com}}{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://github.com/JW-Flo/Project-Ignite/blob/bcc8b784cac1d7962ed21c17e65e0b28a3998130/mcp-mobile/wrangler.toml#L18-L25"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 \ul \ulc3 \strokec3 github.com}}.\
